I am a foreign enterprise, how to verify?

NewsBreak is a US-only traffic source, and we primarily work with businesses based in the United States. If you are a foreign enterprise looking to advertise, please email adsupport@newsbreak.com for further assistance and guidance on verification requirements.
I am in Hong Kong, can I run ads with you?
NewsBreak is a US-only traffic source, so we do not have traffic outside the US. Unfortunately, this means you won't be able to run ads with us from Hong Kong.
I am in Hong Kong but I sell to the US?

If your business is targeting US customers, you can still run ads on NewsBreak. However, please ensure that your business complies with all US advertising regulations. If you need assistance with setting up your account or verifying your business, feel free to reach out to adsupport@newsbreak.com.
